                   //LANGUAGE MODELS
Language models are Ai systems designed to process,generate and understand natural language text.
//LLMS
//Chat Models
LLMs: General purpose models that is used for raw text generation.They take a string(or plain text)
as input and returns a string(plain text).Older models not used now.

Chat Models:Language models that are specialised for conversational tasks.They take a sequence of messages
as inputs and return chat messages as outputs( as opposed to using plain text).
These are traditionally newer models and used in comparison to the LLMs.
